claim.claim-text:
A method of automated driving control for a vehicle (1), comprising:
making the vehicle (1) drive automatically;
detecting holding of a steering wheel by a driver;
detecting an operation of an accelerator pedal by the driver; and
cancelling the automated driving of the vehicle (1) and controlling the vehicle (1) at least according to the operation of the accelerator pedal in the case where the driver holds the steering wheel and the driver operates the accelerator pedal while the vehicle (1) is made to drive automatically.
